{
  "stem": "752.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Later, while we were touring Russia, they told us that he heard that I am touring, at that time, my husband.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he wanna to meet me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he got shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This I find out from a friend.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When he ran away from the [NON-ENGLISH], you know, from the-- he got shot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A year and a half.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got married the 29th of June, 1941 in Lviv.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just no man-- no no wedding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- just a man performed at the the the wedding ceremony.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And two days after, we left for Romania, for Chernivtsi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in Chernivtsi, when we arrived was again the-- the meeting place from all refugees was in cafe houses.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So all--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--all the whispers, and all the news, what's goin' on in the world-- one had a radio.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One had this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One had that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That we better proceed further, because the Germans already declared war on Russia on the first of July, two days after we arrive.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my husband knew Russian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he had a very good position in-- in the government.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because it was announced in a paper, who knows Russian to come to this and this place, that they can help us make a living.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- excuse me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my husband went and he got a very good position with his Russian language.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I kept on working in that cafeteria in the theater-- in the Grand Opera in Lviv, in the cafeteria.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wasn't an opera singer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Now, you said that this was after Romania?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, this is in Romania.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Chernivtsi.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Chernivtsi what belonged at that time to Romania.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Russian, the Russian were there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's why we went there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after the-- the Germans declared together war on Russia, we proceed further to Samarkand.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
